"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T21:01:44.000Z","msg":"只係對唔耐熱既病菌有效，中共肺炎嚟自蝙蝠，而蝙蝠體溫長期45度以上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}